data.description: This charming 3 bed, 2 bath, is located in Deer Meadow & feeds into Burleson ISD!  This home boasts an office adorned with a rustic barn door. A versatile flex space that can serve as a cozy living area or playroom. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, the 1-year old electric range that doubles as an air fryer or double oven, with a transferable 5yr warranty. The eat-in kitchen features a spacious area for casual dining, complemented by a large window that floods the space with natural light & provides a delightful view of the backyard. LED lighting adorns the entirety of the home, with optional color-changing bulbs in the secondary bedrooms & the 2nd living area. The backyard boasts 2-covered patio areas ideal for entertaining guests. Also, the open land behind the backyard ensures peace while enjoying outdoor activities. Conveniently located near HWY 35, shopping, dining, entertainment, and only a 5-minute walk to the community park down the street!
